lead_paragraph: Bartolo Colon pitched seven strong innings and Curtis Granderson set the tone with a leadoff home run as the New York Mets defeated the Milwaukee Brewers 5-2 on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Colon Pitches 7 Strong Innings as Mets Beat Brewers 5-2
